{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-30-1",
 "title": "Cleared to Leave Dreven",
 "summary": "Held under guard at the Admiral Bevven Spaceport on the Imperial capital of Dreven, the disguised NRI agent Bazil McKenzie (as Mege Vauki) seethes silently while the armored Imperial commander Zeak approaches. Agitated after being reprimanded by his own superiors for grounding the freighter without proper orders, Zeak abruptly orders Bazil and his crew off the planet, their repaired ship and cargo returned intact, with a warning never to come back. Bazil masks his anger behind sudden, almost sickening courtesy, thanking the commander profusely before boarding the Triton. Escorted out by TIE Interceptors and cleared past the gravity well, the freighter jumps to hyperspace on a heading toward Tatooine.",
